{
  "text": "Regarding the retentive force provided by clasps, authors stated that the retentive force for a cast clasp should be at least 4-5 N. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] However, the retentive force in our study ranging from 4 to 17 N [ Table 3 ].",
